Director, Finance at Discovery Networks Asia-Pacific in Singapore - Job | LinkedIn
Director, Finance - SingaporePosted 1 day agoExperienceDirectorJob functionFinanceEmployment typeFull-timeIndustryBroadcast MediaJob ID13666994This is a preview of the Director, Finance job at Discovery Networks Asia-Pacific. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!About this jobJob descriptionYou will provide support to SVP & CFO, Finance & Corporate Operations in regular and normal business relating to Finance. You are required to stay updated on the current regulations affecting the industry and effects upon the company. Be responsible in delivering quality management information and reviewing budget processes and forecasts. You will lead a team to achieve department and business finance demands with a high degree of sensitivity and confidentiality. Key Responsibilities
• Oversee the smooth and efficient running of Finance Department.
• Ensure compliance with statutory authority and audit requirements.
• Maintain integrity of Accounting system (software), ensuring it remains effective and operational at all times.
• Ensure all legislative requirements are complied with at all times
• Conduct balance sheet reconciliation for review on a monthly basis.
• Ensure monthly reconciliation of all ledgers and sub-ledgers. Analyze business performance/ results and providing feedback to Senior Management.
• Track and monitor revenue for accuracy, verifying it against sub ledger report on a monthly basis. Ensure monthly accruals are adjusted to meet demands of the business.
• Co-ordinate and prepare annual finance budgets. Ensure the accurate preparation / reporting of monthly financial results in strict accordance with Company deadlines. Ensure any variations to budgets and forecasts are explained in management reports, including any future / potential exposures to the organization.
• Collate all relevant information to produce end of year statutory accounts for the company. Ensure that end of year statutory accounts report is finalized by specified date and presented to management for review. On a monthly basis track and review expenditure against set budgets.
• Ensure that relevant information is communicated to direct reports enabling them to effectively carry out their functions. Delegate tasks to direct reports in line with skill, knowledge and ability and where necessary identify skill gaps and training requirements. As required, become involved in relevant personnel matters including recruitment, termination and counseling. Complete KPI assessment of direct reports within Company specified time frame.
• Lead implementation of a SOX compliant environment including critical path, status and management reporting internally and externally. Liaison point for Internal and External Audit. This position will be based in Singapore.Desired Skills and Experience• CPA with 10 years’ experience financial accounting.
• Experience in MNCs and APAC regional role.
• Should have proven skills of leading and implementation of projects.
• Excellent communication, written and interpersonal skills.
• Maturity to lead and build rapport in a culturally diverse environment.
• Independent, highly analytical and having a keen eye for detail.
• Knowledge of SOX and US GAAP highly desirable.
• Proficiency in Microsoft Office and SAP.About this companyDiscovery Networks Asia-PacificDiscovery Networks Asia-Pacific (DNAP) is a leading provider of non-fiction entertainment that empowers people to explore their world and satisfy their curiosity through its portfolio of eight high quality brands, including Discovery Channel, Animal Planet, TLC, Discovery Science, Discovery Home & Health, Discovery Turbo, Discovery HD World, and Discovery Kids.   To support DNAP’s growth in the region, we invite dynamic and result-oriented individuals to apply for this position. Successful candidates can look forward to an attractive compensation and benefits package that commensurate with experience and qualifications.   To know more about Discovery, please visit our websites: http://corporate.discovery.com/ http://asia.discovery.com/Similar jobsSingaporePosted 11 days agoSingaporePosted 27 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 14 days agoSingaporePosted 27 days agoSingaporePosted 1 day agoSingaporePosted 1 day agoApeldoorn Area…Posted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 22 days agoIndiaPosted 1 day agoThis is a preview of the Director, Finance job at Discovery Networks Asia-Pacific. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!People also searchedPeople also viewedSingaporePosted 11 days agoSingaporePosted 27 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 14 days agoSingaporePosted 27 days agoSingaporePosted 1 day agoSingaporePosted 1 day agoApeldoorn Area, NetherlandsPosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 22 days agoIndiaPosted 1 day ago
